{"tid":2044970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國示威咪證明美國人質素高過支那人","createTime":"2020-05-31T12:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T15:48:13.000Z","uid":36775,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"93008c29a380d64dc1b92c8fae09158ba12c9447","tid":2044970,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"唔計looting果堆<br />\n一個國家唔同族裔都出來示威爭取種族平等<br />\n就能夠證明呢個國家係文明國家<br />\n望下西藏新疆，支共做乜支那人都扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至支持支共去滅人族<br />\n<br />\n呢啲咪文明國家同野蠻国家分別<br />\n後者好明顯民智未開，個腦開發得一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲停留响小農DNA，更加證明支那民族適合圈養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 全世界警暴都係仆街<br />\n特別係香港身受其害<br />\n更加要反警暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf687ea1a1027ed57350d0810693cfd35ef8be3","tid":2044970,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:55:44.000Z","msg":"早你十年啊濛撚<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/乌鲁木齐七五事件\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E4%B9%8C%E9%B2%81%E6%9C%A8%E9%BD%90%E4%B8%83%E4%BA%94%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=00f3cc07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/乌鲁木齐七五事件</a>"},{"pid":"eaf51dae1efc040fc9ad43a246ed12dffc7247cd","tid":2044970,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:26:22.000Z","msg":"高質過香港人先"},{"pid":"83ec0a475126608bcebb1967e283d8b2ca9642cc","tid":2044970,"uid":263183,"like":0,"di